      "content": "i know there are hotlines, i've seen them, but they don't change the fact that my life is basically over. it's not just sadness, it's like the air is gone. i look at my apartment and it's just empty. there's no future here. i don't even see the point in trying to \"process\" it when the person i was with is just... gone. everything feels completely hollow.",
